OL,3,CBoy, 13, ends up in A&E on drip as
OL,4,Cwater contamination scandal continues
OL,6,FThe family of a 13-year-old boy in
OL,7,Fsouth Devon who was taken to A&E with
OL,8,Fsevere sickness, diarrhoea and
OL,9,Fdehydration have hit out at South West
OL,10,FWater over water contamination in
OL,11,FBrixham.
OL,13,FA boil notice has been put in place
OL,14,Ffor thousands of people living in
OL,15,FBrixham after the parasite
OL,16,Fcryptosporidium was found in the water.
