OL,6,FThe UK Health Security Agency has so
OL,7,Ffar confirmed 46 cases of the parasite
OL,8,F- which causes diarrhoea and vomiting
OL,9,F- but more than 100 further people
OL,10,Fhave reported similar symptoms.
OL,12,FKayley Lewis, who lives in Brixham,
OL,13,Fsaid her 13-year-old son Jacob ended
OL,14,Fup in A&E after suffering vomiting,
OL,15,Fdiarrhoea and dehydration.
OL,17,FShe said: "He was sick and had
OL,18,Fdiarrhoea. Because he was so
OL,19,Fdehydrated, he had to go on an IV drip
OL,20,Fand they kept him in overnight until
OL,21,Fhe was well enough.
