OL,6,F"His blood pressure kept going really
OL,7,Flow too, it affected his whole body."
OL,9,FSouth West Water has apologised to
OL,10,Fpeople affected and says they will all
OL,11,Freceive #115 in compensation.
OL,13,FThe firm says it is working closely
OL,14,Fwith the UK Health Security Agency and
OL,15,Fpublic health partners to "urgently
OL,16,Finvestigate" how cryptosporidium is
OL,17,Fgetting into its network so it can be
OL,18,Ffixed.
