OL,3,CBoy, 13, ends up in A&E on drip as
OL,4,Cwater contamination scandal continues
OL,6,FChief Executive Susan Davy said:
OL,7,F"While incidents like these are
OL,8,Fthankfully very rare, our customers
OL,9,Fexpect a safe, clean, and reliable
OL,10,Fsource of drinking water. I know on
OL,11,Fthis occasion we have fallen
OL,12,Fsignificantly short of what you expect
OL,13,Fof us."
OL,15,FShe added: "All of us at South West
OL,16,FWater live and work in the region,
OL,17,Fjust like you. It is our home and a
OL,18,Fplace we love. I am sorry this has
OL,19,Fhappened.
