OL,6,F"I promise you that we will not stop
OL,7,Fworking until the situation has been
OL,8,Fresolved and drinking water returns to
OL,9,Fthe quality level you expect."
OL,11,FHowever, Kayley told ITV News she does
OL,12,Fnot accept South West Water's apology
OL,13,Fover the issue.
OL,15,FShe said: "I don't think it's good
OL,16,Fenough, considering how much we're
OL,17,Fhaving to boil the water and go and
OL,18,Fbuy our own water.
