OL,7,F"The past few days have been
OL,8,Fhorrendous. Yesterday the school shut
OL,9,Fso we've had children to look after
OL,10,Ftoo."
OL,12,FLike Kayley, Tanya doesn't accept the
OL,13,Fapology from South West Water.
OL,15,FShe said there's been a delay in
OL,16,Fcommunication.
