OL,6,F"I posted on social media on Tuesday
OL,7,F14 May and that blew up overnight.
OL,8,FThey tested on Wednesday, told me it
OL,9,Fwould be 24 hours before the results
OL,10,Fwould come back - but they were still
OL,11,Ftelling people water was safe to drink.
OL,13,F"They should have told people to boil
OL,14,Fthe water sooner."
OL,16,FIn terms of the #115 in compensation,
