OL,8,Fwithout needing medical advice.
OL,10,F"Those affected should stay off school
OL,11,Fand work for 48hrs since the last
OL,12,Fepisode of illness and away from
OL,13,Fswimming pools for 14 days after the
OL,14,Flast episode of illness."
